# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and on checkout. Without this, a
# Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) gets CRLF working-tree bytes, which makes
# the content-addressed file-guard and biome report false drift locally — the LF
# baseline is what CI computes. This makes the gates runnable correctly on any OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Append-only audit log: union-merge kills tail conflicts (ADR-0007).
docs/audit-history.ndjson merge=union
# Visual-regression baselines are binary.
*.png binary
